<HEADLINE> Yugoslavia to Follow EU Standards on Ethnic Minorities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, May 6 (Xinhua) -- Yugoslavia on Wednesday promised to
follow the standards set by the European Union (EU) on the rights
