with the previous price of 312,875 pesos, which was in force
since April 28.
</P>
<P>
The Colombian coffee authorties decided to freeze domestic
coffee price in consideration of a decrease in quotations of
the international markets.
</P>
<P>
The national committee has been adjusting domestic coffee
price twice per week, according to coffee prices of the
international markets. 
